  "body": "# Info\nThis resourcepack contains all my previous core shaders that are in their own packs. Normally you wouldn't be able to combine them together so thats what this resourcepack is for.\n\n### How to config\nIf you want to disable some of the packs embedded in this you can do so in the settings file.\nThe settings file can be found at \"assets/bluebird/shaders/include/settings.glsl\".\nIn order to change the settings, just change true to false or vice versa next to the variables (**Case Sensitive**).\n\n# Embedded in this pack\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/emissive-office-cape\">\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/HdOx2YHC/cf95c8b4178ded5eeaac680be4098458455c1cc4_96.webp\" alt=\"Emissive Office Cape\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\">\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/emissive-trims\">\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/gxUihgVw/fc96bb5326578f80b1a245ecce2555373d47cdef.png\" alt=\"Emissive Trims\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\">\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/emissive-cape-portals\">\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/K0psvV8X/34840719349cbcdafe8e4e78ec02c8253256ada4.png\" alt=\"Emissive Cape portals\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\">\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/emissive-twitch-cape\">\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/dpiEWPp1/c3315e8bbbc049400a2166d5fb218cac8047365d_96.webp\" alt=\"Emissive Twitch Cape\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\">\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/i-am-not-steve\">\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/SxpRZYW5/d282e7848bca5aab9bc969480d200f3c09c137b6_96.webp\" alt=\"I am not steve\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\">\n</a>",
